Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hình như là tới-{Seems I managed to re-}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, sao thế?{Reg, what's wrong?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Có gì đó...{Something has...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,bắt lấy...{grabbed...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,tay tớ.{my arms.}
